latestPosts.caption:
After two years of existance, our beautylounge @leboudoirdens won "BEAUTY AWARD 2018" who qualifies as a TOP of The TOP beauty institut of #PARIS for best client service, best quality of work. 
We dreamt about it but never thought we will get it one day. 
We don't run for sucess, we just love so much what we do and we are extreamly happy that our client finaly feel it and accepted our concept.
The fusion of desi and french culture.
That was our challenge ! 
I don't know what will be my futur but one thing am dame sure, i will never ever forget where am from and who were with me at the beggining. 
My failures are my strongness. 
And one more thing, specialy for all mother around the world. Never think your childs is an obstacle for you. If you really want to archive your dream, GOD will always find a way for you. Never blame your childs. They are blessing of GOD. 
To be a mother and entrepreneur, it's a challenge. 
Prouve yourself that you can do it! 💪🏽
Never leave your family for carrer and vice versa. Be between that and do what you make you happy. If you are happy then the whole world is happy. 
My family, my friends and YOU, my beautiful supporters.
THANK YOU ! ❤️😘💪🏽🏆 ▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️▫️
